BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:-3LIcrU6C1rWiDl7vSUWg
SUMMARY:Shen Yun 2026
DTSTAMP:20260401T021317Z
DTSTART:20260405T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:The gong resounds\, the curtain opens\, and fairies emerge from
	 a sea of billowing clouds. Mongolians ride on horseback across grasslands
	 as vast as the sky. Dynasties rise and fall—as ancient legends of love\, 
	loss\, humor and valor unfold before your eyes.\n\nhttps://www.seattlecent
	er.com/events/event-calendar/shen-yun-2026-x47083\n\nFrom Seattle Center E
	vents
URL:https://www.seattlecenter.com/events/event-calendar/shen-yun-2026-x4708
	3
LOCATION:Marion Oliver McCaw Hall
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seattle-center-events
CATEGORIES:Seattle Center Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
